| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4409 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7eeb74c6-562d-531d-8ac1-9839cc7645d4"
